6.3451, 166.7411, 167.1125, 168.572, 167.0253, 166.5206, 166.8226, 165.802, 165.0719, 165.4867, 165.1275, 165.5651, 165.0774, 164.3985, 164.2565, 164.9633, 163.7907, 163.0192, 162.5223, 163.0139, 163.7278, 163.8299, 164.6004, 164.9703, 164.8781, 165.9447, 167.0316, 167.3636, 168.2916, 168.4602, 168.8334, 168.9578, 168.98, 167.5888, 168.11, 168.2364, 168.4727, 168.2411, 168.6335, 167.8978, 167.5887, 168.6513, 169.8649, 168.4834, 168.3932, 169.9899, 169.5985, 169.3101, 169.9788, 170.0256, 168.844, 168.1779, 168.2002, 167.7794, 168.3959, 167.9442, 166.1669, 166.0981, 166.1016, 167.2632, 167.6117, 168.0428, 169.0466, 168.7241, 169.1334, 168.5637, 168.7615, 169.5828, 169.1577, 170.5695, 170.0391, 168.7613, 168.9214, 168.1976, 169.0672, 169.1513, 168.5955, 169.0678, 168.9952, 169.3207, 168.4843, 170.2025, 170.6109, 170.0001, 169.2074, 169.4551, 169.5982, 169.0649, 167.676, 167.5453, 168.3634, 168.0786, 169.4057, 169.8283, 171.2833, 170.6621, 170.6729, 170.8146, 169.2838, 168.3441, 167.8149, 166.1422, 167.3915, 168.5525, 166.525, 167.4937, 167.6301, 166.2226, 167.6063, 166.0998, 165.8689, 165.6176, 163.4596, 162.4807, 163.5179, 162.6891, 160.2791, 162.8556, 163.1053, 162.0516, 164.9202, 164.5662, 163.8141, 163.7983, 164.1287, 161.2799, 162.9162, 163.0924, 163.1533, 162.5585, 165.9632, 164.389, 163.0394, 163.0546, 165.4238, 165.0681, 164.7466, 165.3685, 164.4934, 164.3186, 164.9741, 164.318, 162.7375, 162.9634, 163.6347, 168.0845, 173.3216, 171.4238, 173.8608, 174.2296, 176.2847, 174.135, 173.7911, 175.0675, 175.3211, 175.9983, 177.0616, 178.5207, 183.9185, 180.7038, 178.2961, 178.6154, 176.7884, 177.8104, 177.1856, 177.6097, 177.9284, 177.9312, 178.1211, 177.3434, 177.4131, 177.2395, 176.8681, 176.8687, 176.8134, 177.0048, 177.1135, 176.5624, 176.8409, 176.3343, 176.2805, 175.3414, 175.8868, 176.2737, 175.1125, 176.114, 176.2213, 176.4872, 176.7338, 176.8633], "summary_html": "<h1>GP遗传规划截面因子 | Sharpe 1.254 | 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略复现中信期货利用遗传规划(Genetic Programming)在商品期货截面上挖掘的5个alpha因子。GP通过对OHLCV、持仓量、仓单等11个原始特征进行时序算子嵌套组合（如滚动均值、标准差、RSI、KAMA、相关系数、协方差等），自动搜索出具有截面选期能力的复合公式树。5个因子分别捕捉了量价相关性振荡(Alpha1)、仓单极值归一化(Alpha2)、持仓量自适应均线RSI(Alpha3)、量价相关稳定性(Alpha4)、开盘价与成交量协方差(Alpha5)。每日对因子值进行截面排名，做多高分组、做空低分组，构建多空组合。</p>\n<p>策略赚钱的核心逻辑：多因子等权组合（排除了表现最差的Alpha1）可以从多维度捕捉商品期货截面价值差异，通过截面标准化(CS)归一化进一步增强信号稳定性，不同因子间低相关性提供了分散化收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.0</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.48</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.4 / 0.96</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.04</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.09</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td><td>1.23</td><td>1.17</td><td>1.77</td><td>0.36</td><td>0.77</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.87</span></td><td>1.13</td><td>1.84</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.1</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.01</span></td><td>1.19</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.51</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>vwap</code></td><td>VWAP</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 7 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 7 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>5个因子的GP公式树：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha1} = \\text{ts\\_midpoint}\\big(\\text{ts\\_pct\\_change}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_AROONOSC}(V, P_{vwap}, 10), 10\\big), 5\\big), 486\\big) \\quad (\\text{正向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha2} = \\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}\\big(\\text{ts\\_maxmin}(W, 126), 126\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha3} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_sum}\\big(\\text{ts\\_rsi}\\big(\\text{ts\\_kama}(OI, 486), 63\\big), 243\\big), 63\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha4} = \\text{ts\\_ema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_inverse\\_cv}\\big(\\text{ts\\_corr}(V, P_{vwap}, 21), 42\\big), 105\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Alpha5} = \\text{ts\\_dema}\\big(\\text{ts\\_median}\\big(\\text{ts\\_cov}(P_{open}, V, 21), 21\\big), 15\\big) \\quad (\\text{负向})</div>\n<p>其中：<span class=\"math-tex\">V</span> = volume, <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{vwap}</span> = vwap, <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> = receipt(仓单), <span class=\"math-tex\">OI</span> = opi(持仓量), <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{open}</span> = open</p>\n<p><strong>关键算子定义</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li><code>ts_inverse_cv(X, d)</code> = rolling_mean(X,d) / rolling_std(X,d)</li>\n<li><code>ts_maxmin(X, d)</code> = (X - rolling_min(X,d)) / (rolling_max(X,d) - rolling_min(X,d))</li>\n<li><code>ts_AROONOSC(X1, X2, d)</code> = Aroon振荡器（近似：两变量在窗口内的相对位置差）</li>\n<li><code>ts_kama(X, d)</code> = Kaufman自适应移动均线</li>\n<li><code>ts_dema(X, d)</code> = 2*EMA(X,d) - EMA(EMA(X,d),d)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>: Combo = 等权平均(Alpha2_rank, Alpha3_rank, Alpha4_rank, Alpha5_rank)，截面标准化后做多空。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.98)</strong>: 实现全部5个GP因子，Alpha2(仓单极值)最强(0.98)，Alpha1(Aroon)反向(-0.45)。诊断发现combo有潜力但受Alpha1拖累。 - 诊断: Alpha1 Aroon振荡器近似不够准确，或方向判断有误 - 行动: 计划R2排除Alpha1，聚焦combo和Alpha2</p>\n<p>2. <strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.21)</strong>: 排除Alpha1后的4因子combo+截面标准化(CS)大幅提升。combo_H5_cs达1.21，比单因子alpha2(0.98)提升24%。CS归一化普遍优于raw和ts。 - 诊断: CS归一化明显有效，hold期可进一步优化 - 行动: R3扩展hold期搜索，加IC门控</p>\n<p>3. <strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.25)</strong>: Hold=7天略优于5天(1.254 vs 1.213)，IC门控未带来额外提升（combo已足够稳定）。多个变体Sharpe&gt;1.0，信号稳健。 - 关键转折: 从单因子Alpha2到4因子combo+CS归一化，Sharpe从0.98提升至1.25</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个有效品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 7天换仓（最优），1-10天均可</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面多空</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - Alpha2依赖仓单数据(receipt)，该字段非空率约28%，部分品种缺失时因子退化\n<p>- Alpha1(Aroon振荡器)在本实现中表现为负，可能因Aroon算子的近似偏差 - 年度Sharpe分布不均：2016-2017和2020表现最强，2023-2024略弱 - 高杠杆(CS归一化后名义杠杆&gt;1x)贡献了部分收益</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9989</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.79s</li>\n</ul>"}